## Testing Real-Time Features

```ruby
test "receives real-time notifications" do
  sign_in_as @user
  visit root_url
  
  # Trigger notification in background
  Notification.create!(user: @user, message: "New comment")
  
  # Wait for WebSocket to deliver
  assert_selector ".notification", text: "New comment", wait: 3
end
```

